<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to the Holding Pattern analysis toolkit!</h1>
<br />
<h4>Below you can read about the different tools available:</h4>

<div class="list-group">
    <a href="FlightVisualizer" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start">
        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
            <h5 class="mb-2">Flight Visualizer</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-2">
            This tool allows you the see the route a individual flight has taken and whether or not a holding pattern occurred.
        </p>
    </a>
    <a href="massdetection" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start">
        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
